@startuml
title 미핏 - 이력서 분석 시퀀스 (Frontend → Backend → analysis-resume Worker)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #555555
  LifeLineBorderColor #2196F3
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  ParticipantBorderColor #2196F3
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
}

actor "사용자" as U
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Backend" as BE
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "S3 (be-files)" as S3
queue "Redis\nanalysis-resume 큐" as Q
participant "analysis-resume\nWorker" as Worker
participant "OpenAI" as LLM

== A. 파일 업로드 경로 (PDF / DOCX) ==

U -> FE : 파일 선택 + 업로드
FE -> BE : POST /resumes/ (type=file)
activate BE
  BE -> S3 : 원본 파일 업로드
  BE -> DB : Resume(status=DRAFT) 생성
  BE -> BE : FinalizeResumeService\n(자동 호출)
  BE -> DB : status = ANALYZING
  BE -> Q : dispatch analysis tasks
  BE --> FE : { uuid }
deactivate BE

FE -> FE : SSE 구독\n/sse/resumes/{uuid}/analysis-status/

== B. 분석 워커 처리 ==

Q -> Worker : pull task
activate Worker

Worker -> S3 : 원본 다운로드
Worker -> Worker : ExtractTextTask\n(PyPDF / docx2txt)

note right of Worker
  병렬 fork:
end note

par 임베딩
  Worker -> LLM : OpenAI Embedding API
  LLM --> Worker : vector[1536]
else LLM 파싱
  Worker -> LLM : gpt-4o-mini\n(이력서 → 구조화 JSON)
  LLM --> Worker : { skills, experience, ... }
end

Worker -> Worker : FinalizeResumeTask (join)
Worker -> Q : Backend 콜백 task\nApplyAnalysisResultTask
deactivate Worker

== C. Backend 콜백 ==

Q -> BE : pull callback
activate BE
  BE -> DB : Resume 섹션 저장 (Experience, Skill, ...)
  BE -> DB : ResumeEmbedding 저장
  BE -> DB : status = COMPLETED
  BE -> DB : TokenUsage.log()
deactivate BE

== D. SSE 알림 ==

BE -> FE : SSE event { status: COMPLETED }
FE -> BE : GET /resumes/{uuid}/
BE --> FE : 전체 이력서 데이터

U <- FE : "분석 완료" 배지 + 상세 페이지

footer MeFit - 이력서 분석 (analysis-resume 도메인)
@enduml
